H2.text: what is the cross on a letter t called. Stroke

H3.text: what is the cross on a letter t called. arm

A4.text: In typeface anatomy, crossbar refers to some types of horizontal strokes

A5.text: Strokes that connect, as in A and H, or cross other strokes, as in t, are also known as crossbars.

A6.text: A longer horizontal stroke at the top or bottom, as in E T, is an arm.
